  "3099830": {
    "name": "P.R.D.A.",
    "steam_appid": 3099830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/dbd36d61d155af618a3b83f39abaef91.avif?t=1772369350\" width=1280 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《P.R.D.A.》是一款带有搜打撤元素的roguelike卡牌构筑游戏，你将扮演一名来自超自然研究与防御机构（简称P.R.D.A.）的探员，处理世界各地的扭曲生物。制作卡牌来构筑你的牌组，尽可能收集对你有利的塔罗牌。请谨慎选择，因为你的选择可能会使敌人获益。但也不必担心失败，因为你击败的每个敌人都有可能成为下一局游戏的资源，你可以用它来让自己更加强大。努力完成你的任务，探员。这将是一次艰难的冒险。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/7639b7eed0c7fbc3410f2f118bb31a90.avif?t=1772369350\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras_big/7639b7eed0c7fbc3410f2f118bb31a90.webp?t=1772369350 width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>自定义开局角色与初始牌组</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色具备不同的基因效果，每种基因效果提供多个可选的卡牌效果，依据角色各自拥有的卡牌模板，将选择的效果与模板组合，从而创建自定义的初始牌组。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/02eeeff72cfd4b5bfe39da3293e356bf.poster.avif?t=1772369350\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/02eeeff72cfd4b5bfe39da3293e356bf.webm?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/02eeeff72cfd4b5bfe39da3293e356bf.mp4?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>制作独特效果的自定义卡牌</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用游戏过程中收集到的效果词条，将不同效果进行排列组合，从而制作出拥有强大效果的独特卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/10cda1186e101e0eec434a031bc16432.poster.avif?t=1772369350\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/10cda1186e101e0eec434a031bc16432.webm?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/10cda1186e101e0eec434a031bc16432.mp4?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>探索不同路线</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内每个地区拥有各自不同的地区效果，不同的路线则会决定接下来的遭遇，如何规划前进路线将会是个挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/05236415d142020251b38dca51a6f912.poster.avif?t=1772369350\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/05236415d142020251b38dca51a6f912.webm?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/05236415d142020251b38dca51a6f912.mp4?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>击败敌人获取资源</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一般、精英和BOSS，不同的怪物将会带来不同的挑战和资源，击败这些敌人来收集制作卡牌的资源，收集道具牌与塔罗牌来逐步构建自己的游玩策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/0bb108376383faf33c87a2daaf619f9b.poster.avif?t=1772369350\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/0bb108376383faf33c87a2daaf619f9b.webm?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/0bb108376383faf33c87a2daaf619f9b.mp4?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>从任务中撤离</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你对继续前进感到压力时，寻找撤离点将会是更好的选择，利用撤离点将过程中的资源带出，从而在新一局的游戏中继续使用它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/18f9ca801590b16e5700355df7b3c605.poster.avif?t=1772369350\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/18f9ca801590b16e5700355df7b3c605.webm?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/18f9ca801590b16e5700355df7b3c605.mp4?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>独特的塔罗牌系统</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败精英敌人时，可以为自己和敌人分别选择一张塔罗牌，塔罗牌会为其持有者施加特殊效果，每张塔罗牌在正、逆位状态下均拥有不同的特殊效果，如何组织与搭配敌我双方的塔罗牌将会是胜利与否的关键要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/a8c3af3be4828e9120fa58efa90519ca.poster.avif?t=1772369350\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/a8c3af3be4828e9120fa58efa90519ca.webm?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099830/extras/a8c3af3be4828e9120fa58efa90519ca.mp4?t=1772369350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
